==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: meals-on-wheels
<hw>meals-on-wheels</hw></mhw>
<pos>n.</pos> <def>A program that delivers hot meals to persons, such as
the elderly or disabled, who are confined to their homes and unable to
cook for themselves; also, the meals thus delivered. Such programs are
usually conducted by governmental or charitable organizations.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

